    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 3.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い立派な寮……\nというより、シェアハウスですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wow‚ what a big dorm.\nI’d say it’s more of a “share-house.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "東京に拠点を移してから、メンバーみんな週の大半は\nここで生活してるんだよ……それより",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since we moved operations to Tokyo‚\neveryone lives here most of the time. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 17.566666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！\nこ、こっちですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}!\nTh-this way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、すず！\n事件って、一体何が……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong‚ Suzu?!\nWhat’s this “big problem” you mentioned?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、{user}さん\n見て見て、段ボールの中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ {user}‚\nJust look inside this box.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.333333333333,
          "startTime": 30.933333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みゃ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meowww.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？　…………猫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? A cat?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "近くに捨てられていたのを\n芽衣ちゃんが保護したんだそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Somebody abandoned it nearby\nso Mei-chan rescued it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、凄く可愛くって\nかわいそうだったんだもん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was just so cute!\nAnd I felt sorry for the poor thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "猫を保護？　まさか、それが事件の正体？\nなんだ……良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You rescued a cat? Wait a minute‚ is this the “big problem”?\nOh… what a relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "よ、良くありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it is most certainly not a relief!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私、捨て猫を拾ったことなんてありませんもの……\nどうしてあげたらいいんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never taken care of a stray cat before.\nHow are we supposed to take care of it?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ、すずちゃん\n今、いろいろ調べている所ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry‚ Suzu-chan.\nI’m looking up a few things right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6666666666686,
          "startTime": 63.233333333333334
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.3333333333344,
          "startTime": 64.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？\nそういえば、一緒にいる女の人……誰？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nBy the way‚ who’s that lady with you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、自己紹介遅くなりました！\n本日付けで星見プロに入社しました、橋本さとみです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Forgive me for my late introductions!\nStarting today‚ I'm employed at Hoshimi Productions. I'm Satomi Hashimoto!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしたのね？\nなら私もご挨拶しませんと……んんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\nThen I’d better introduce myself as well! Hem-hem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私は成宮すず。あの長瀬麻奈様に続く\n第二の『星降る奇跡』と名高いアイドルですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Suzu Narumiya. Following the footsteps of Mana Nagase-sama‚\nI'm the 'The Next Miracle of the Star'!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、その肩書き、いつの間に受け継いで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ when did you give yourself that title…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrsuz-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 98.2
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 98.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん知ってます！　富豪のご令嬢でありながら\nトップアイドルを目指す月スト最年少アイドル！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I know of you! The heiress to a wealthy family‚\nand aims to become a top idol‚ Moon Tempest’s youngest idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrmei-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 107.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "つかみ所のないそぶりが評判の\n天真爛漫アイドル、早坂芽衣ちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ known for her enigmatic behavior‚\nthe innocent idol‚ Mei Hayasaka…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrski-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg5",
      "startTime": 114.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんのお姉さんであり、月ストのまとめ役でも\nあるしっかり者アイドル、白石沙季ちゃんですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Chisa’s big sister and Moon Tempest’s peacemaker‚\nthe diligent idol‚ Saki Shiraishi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 123.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 123.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……ず、ずいぶん勉強熱心……ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Q-quite the study you are… indeed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの場合、半分は趣味なんだそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In Hashimoto-san’s case‚ it’s partly for her hobby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、雫ちゃんと同志\n……ということですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ she’s Shizuku-chan’s people.\nAm I right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうなんだ！\nよろしくね、橋本さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! Yeah‚ I get it!\nNice to meet you‚ Hashimoto-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n……そういえば、他のお二人はどちらでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nCome to think of it‚ where are the other two?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと渚ちゃんなら\n買い物に行ってもらっています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you mean Kotono-chan and Nagisa-chan‚\nthey’re out shopping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
